==Portfolio investments==
Apollo has been an active private equity investor through the [[private equity in the 21st century|mid-2000s buyout boom]].  The following is a list of Apollo's most recent and currently active private equity investments.  The bulk of these investments are held in Apollo Investment Fund V, VI and VII.

